{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at 15, I was doing this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At one-- OK, and things, as, as she started working, she would the next day, right away, they steal, in between their clothes, a little piece of cloth for a kerchief.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she would bring out a, a babushka to cover my bare head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the next day, maybe something else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They always try to steal something out of the-- what you may call the shop.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And their life was normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They got-- we got decent food in there, and a piece of bread, and margarine with that, and something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we would come back to the barrack, 6 o'clock or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "At one point, we are doing this, and everything is in a-- normal as can be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We separate each other every morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She goes to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we go with the other transport, and we go through this gate from Plaszow, which you saw it in a Schindler story.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we go out of that gate to where the German soldiers have the barns for the horses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was-- I wasn't actually near Krakau, where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were marched, always walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one day-- this is already-- we're in there in June.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it's very, very warm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they give us, I think, a half-an-hour rest period, where we ate, like, lunch.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was so hot that we sort of-- us go behind a wagon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's where we settled down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's where we're sitting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we didn't get up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Exact a half hour, we just sat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I guess everybody was tired.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we-- and we just sat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we had a terrible, terrible German soldier who was watching us with two dogs constantly.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
